---
import LandingLayout from "../layouts/LandingLayout.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<LandingLayout
  title="Affordable Mental Health Care in Lexington, Kentucky | Twilight Psychology"
  description="Twilight Psychology provides affordable mental health care in Lexington, Kentucky, including therapy, psychological evaluations, and medication management for new and returning clients."
>
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden px-4 py-20 sm:py-28">
    <div
      class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 opacity-60"
      aria-hidden="true"
      style="background: radial-gradient(90% 70% at 50% 0%, rgba(165,180,252,0.18) 0%, rgba(2,6,23,0) 70%);"
    ></div>

    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-5xl">
      <p class="inline-block rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-4 py-1 text-xs font-black tracking-[0.2em] text-site-sub uppercase">
        Kentucky Mental Health Care
      </p>

      <h1 class="mt-6 font-serif text-4xl font-black tracking-tight text-site-text sm:text-6xl">
        Affordable Mental Health Care in Kentucky
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-base leading-relaxed text-site-sub sm:text-lg">
        Twilight Psychology is focused on delivering affordable, neuro-affirming mental health care for individuals and families in Kentucky.
        Our team offers therapy, psychological testing, and medication management with clear next steps for new clients.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
        <a
          href="/catalog"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-cta px-8 py-3 text-sm font-black text-cta-fg transition hover:bg-cta/80"
        >
          View Services
        </a>
        <a
          href="/resources/new-client"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-(--color-button-border) bg-transparent px-8 py-3 text-sm font-black text-site-text transition hover:bg-white/5"
        >
          New Client Steps
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 pb-20 sm:pb-24">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <article class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-black text-site-text">Testing</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-site-sub">
          Affordable psychological evaluations in Lexington, including ADHD, Autism, and learning assessments.
        </p>
        <a class="mt-5 inline-block text-sm font-black text-cta" href="/services/psychological-evaluations">Explore evaluations</a>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-black text-site-text">Medication</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-site-sub">
          Medication management with personalized support and practical follow-up for long-term mental wellness.
        </p>
        <a class="mt-5 inline-block text-sm font-black text-cta" href="/services/medication-management">Explore medication care</a>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-black text-site-text">Therapy</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-site-sub">
          Evidence-based therapy in Lexington, Kentucky focused on practical progress, emotional safety, and accessible care.
        </p>
        <a class="mt-5 inline-block text-sm font-black text-cta" href="/services/therapy">Explore therapy</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 pb-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 sm:p-10">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-black text-site-text sm:text-4xl">Common Next Steps</h2>
      <ol class="mt-6 grid gap-4 text-sm text-site-sub sm:grid-cols-3">
        <li class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-site-bg/70 p-4">
          <span class="block text-xs font-black tracking-[0.12em] text-site-text uppercase">Step 1</span>
          Review our affordable care options and choose the service that best fits your needs.
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-site-bg/70 p-4">
          <span class="block text-xs font-black tracking-[0.12em] text-site-text uppercase">Step 2</span>
          Check timelines, fees, and insurance details for care in Lexington, Kentucky.
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-site-bg/70 p-4">
          <span class="block text-xs font-black tracking-[0.12em] text-site-text uppercase">Step 3</span>
          Contact us to start intake and schedule your first appointment.
        </li>
      </ol>

      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-cta px-8 py-3 text-sm font-black text-cta-fg transition hover:bg-cta/80"
        >
          Contact Twilight Psychology
        </a>
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-(--color-button-border) bg-transparent px-8 py-3 text-sm font-black text-site-text transition hover:bg-white/5"
        >
          Visit Homepage
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</LandingLayout>
